content:
Unified Knowledge Requirements

Available in: Lightning Experience, Unlimited Edition, and other editions with the Knowledge add-on license.

You must agree to Terms & Conditions in Setup to use Unified Knowledge. Salesforce collaborated with Zoomin to build Unified Knowledge.

Free Trial:
Available for 90 days in your sandbox org and 45 days in your production org, along with three connector instances to third-party knowledge sources.
When the trial expires, third-party knowledge sources stop syncing and content updates no longer appear.
Upgrades from the free trial are purchased directly through Zoomin.

Unified Knowledge requires that Lightning Knowledge is set up in your production org.
To view search results from Unified Knowledge, you need Service Cloud Unlimited Edition or another edition with the Knowledge Add-On license, and assign Knowledge User licenses.
title: Setting Up Unified Knowledge in Service Cloud
